## Generated artifacts
*.pdf
out.json
out.pdf

## ...but the demo output in out/ (JSON + both PDF styles for every bracket size, produced by
## 'brackets all') IS committed so the brackets can be browsed directly on GitHub. Re-include
## the folder and its contents past the '*.pdf' rule above.
!out/
!out/**

## ...but the source project is named Brackets.Pdf; on case-insensitive filesystems
## (Windows/macOS) the '*.pdf' rule above matches that folder, so keep it tracked.
## Re-including just the directory lets git descend; bin/ and obj/ inside it stay ignored.
!src/Brackets.Pdf/

## Rider / VS Code
.idea/
.vscode/
